      <title>特斯拉中国出货量预计将在 2024 年第四次下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/tesla-china-shipments-expected-to-slump-for-fourth-time-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司上海工厂的出货量同比下降 24.2%，这是在中国价格战的影响下这家电动汽车领导者今年产量第四次下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/tesla-china-shipments-expected-to-slump-for-fourth-time-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
